                "invention-title": [
                    "Iron ore pellet with autocatalytic denitration function as well as preparation method and use method of iron ore pellet",
                    "具有自催化脱硝功能的铁矿球团及其制备和使用方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention aims to solve the problems existing in a flue gas NOx control technology in existing pellet production, and provides an iron ore pellet with an autocatalytic denitration function as well as a preparation method and a use method of the iron ore pellet. The method comprises the following steps: uniformly mixing magnetite concentrate, micro-fine particle biomass and bentonite, pelletizing to obtain pellets I, and then adding an organic binder and vanadium-titanium-containing magnetite concentrate to enable the pellets I to continuously grow to obtain pellets II; and preparing oxidized pellets from the pellets II by adopting a chain grate-rotary kiln process. The method has the advantages that a novel structure which internally contains micro-fine particle biomass particles and the micro-fine particle vanadium-titanium magnetite concentrate is adhered to the surface is constructed, carbon and hydrogen components generated by biomass cracking are used as reducing agents, and the coupling catalytic action of iron, vanadium and titanium is utilized, so that economical, efficient and clean autocatalytic denitration in the pellet production process is realized, and the production efficiency is improved. The problems of low denitration efficiency, ammonia escape and the like in ammonia spraying denitration in the pellet production process are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明的目的是为了解决现有球团生产中烟气NOx控制技术存在的问题，提供了一种具有自催化脱硝功能的铁矿球团及其制备和使用方法。该方法将磁铁精矿、微细粒生物质、膨润土进行混匀，造球得到球粒I，然后加入有机粘结剂、含钒钛磁铁精矿让球粒I继续长大得到球粒Ⅱ；将球粒Ⅱ采用链篦机‑回转窑工艺制备氧化球团矿。该方法的优点为：构建内部含有微细粒生物质颗粒、表面粘附微细粒钒钛磁铁精矿的新型结构，利用生物质裂解产生的碳、氢组分作为还原剂以及铁、钒、钛的耦合催化作用，实现球团生产过程经济、高效、清洁自催化脱硝，解决了球团生产过程喷氨脱硝存在脱硝效率低、氨逃逸等问题。"
                }
            ]
